25|$|The Battle <b>of</b> <b>Basra</b> was {{a battle}} of World War I which took place {{south of the city}} <b>of</b> <b>Basra</b> (modern-day Iraq) between British and Ottoman troops from November 11 to November 21, 1914. The battle {{resulted}} in the British capture <b>of</b> <b>Basra.</b>|$|E
